eventName: Ladyish - Techno Night along with the best NZ Female artists.
eventLocation: New Zealand 350 Karangahape Rd Auckland, Auckland 1010
eventInfo:
Belu Colombo and Nolypso are collaborating to bring the first edition of Ladyish, the first Techno Female DJs party in NZ.

With a lineup selected from the best NZ Female Artists, we invite you to immerse yourself in the delights of Techno. Let your senses guide you through an amazing journey from Minimal to Driving and Hard Techno, meaning this for you to dance, move & dive into high energy levels.

Line up coming soon

Event +18 only.

eventLocation: Raynham Park 145 Karangahape Road Auckland, Auckland 1010
eventInfo:
White Night: Arctic Edition invites you to celebrate the end of the winter season. Prepare for an uplifting journey through the many realms of House and Techno music, with one goal: to provide a pure music experience, with pure visuals, pure decor & a pure uplifting party vibe!

We envisage a sea of white so grab your best all-white attire and come let loose to the World of House and Techno.

► Attractions:

✰ Full White UV venue transformation

✰ 5 hours of the best House/Techno Anthems & New Bangers

✰ Twisted Lighting & Visuals

✰ Thumping club sound system

✰ People in white going insane!

This event marks the start of a new chapter and will be the prologue to something even bigger and better!
